  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview:</h2>Enjoy a colorful puzzle-platformer experience in Color Phase! Find and use different colors to interact with the world around you in a variety of different ways to reach your goal!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore 20+ levels solving puzzles and completing dexterous challenges<br></li><li> Utilize four (4) colors each with their own attributes and special ability <br></li><li> There <strong><i>is</i></strong> a grappling hook<br></li><li> This game will not hurt you </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About us:</h2>Developed by Heatwave Studio (formerly 25PercentGames), a student game development group based out of Arizona State University that aims to complete and publish one game each year. The game is a completely volunteer effort from an interdisciplinary team of students from across the academic and creative spectrum. We hope you enjoy what we made!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><strong>Solve puzzles!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.poster.avif?t=1599147364\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.webm?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.mp4?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Navigate platforming challenges!!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/0ae6eea1d18256126774d490f45ba7e8.poster.avif?t=1599147364\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/0ae6eea1d18256126774d490f45ba7e8.webm?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/0ae6eea1d18256126774d490f45ba7e8.mp4?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>I already said there's a grapple hook!!!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/dad8876d63a9b60b83a92225c7ed6463.poster.avif?t=1599147364\" width=666 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/dad8876d63a9b60b83a92225c7ed6463.webm?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/dad8876d63a9b60b83a92225c7ed6463.mp4?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview:</h2>Enjoy a colorful puzzle-platformer experience in Color Phase! Find and use different colors to interact with the world around you in a variety of different ways to reach your goal!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore 20+ levels solving puzzles and completing dexterous challenges<br></li><li> Utilize four (4) colors each with their own attributes and special ability <br></li><li> There <strong><i>is</i></strong> a grappling hook<br></li><li> This game will not hurt you </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About us:</h2>Developed by Heatwave Studio (formerly 25PercentGames), a student game development group based out of Arizona State University that aims to complete and publish one game each year. The game is a completely volunteer effort from an interdisciplinary team of students from across the academic and creative spectrum. We hope you enjoy what we made!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><strong>Solve puzzles!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.poster.avif?t=1599147364\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.webm?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/d0bc7c5b0b950e0064c1b88f8c0e273e.mp4?t=1599147364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Navigate platforming challenges!!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956540/extras/0ae6eea1d18256126774d490f45ba7e8.poster.avif?t=1599147364\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst